cs.AR, cs.EM, cs.SY, cs.SE, cs.PL 

The paper deals with energy consumption of software running on devices, which is a topic that falls under the category of embedded systems (cs.EM) and system-level design and simulation (cs.SY). The use of genetic algorithms for maximizing energy consumption also falls under the category of optimization and control (cs.OH). The paper also discusses the modelling of energy consumption, which falls under the category of programming languages (cs.PL) and architecture (cs.AR).
